        <div xml:id="TK1119">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>malaraṉṉa kaṇṇāḷ mukamotti yāyiṟ </l>
<l>palarkāṇat tōṉṟal mati</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O moon, if you wish to resemble the face of her whose eyes are like (these) flowers, do not appear so as to be seen by all.</l>
